{"tid":871630,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"唱歌技巧小分享 - 唱歌喉嚨好鬼緊 點算好?","createTime":"2018-10-22T05:52:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-22T08:36:40.000Z","uid":153939,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ee948f68691dcb61c4a607f095b2a569154eebce","tid":871630,"uid":153939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T05:52:18.000Z","msg":"我細個唱歌個陣都係同好多人一樣 成日走音 音色好唔穩 唱幾首歌喉嚨就會好緊<br />\n<br />\n但係經過有系統既訓練 終於明白 唱歌其實同做gym 做其他運動一樣 係可以慢慢訓練既 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 需要知道既其實係一個方法 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n方法並唔係不斷不斷地唱歌去令自己進<br />\n<br />\n其中一個有系統既訓練方法其實就係<br />\n-用diaphragm（肚仔呼吸大法）<br />\n<br />\n唱歌所有所有既力量 不論高低音都要用肚嚟support 你幻想 你既肚腩仔就等於一部車既engine <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不論你低音定高音你唔開engine部車係無力跑 特別係上到高音 唔用肚腩係hold唔住既<br />\n<br />\n俾條VIDEO大家睇睇啦<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=J5PxMg14zck&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DJ5PxMg14zck%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=hOZCSuynYZfFE9uXVR4tkdU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=23320ef6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=J5PxMg14zck&amp;feature=youtu.be</a>"},{"pid":"4968b64e1f5c6e65d103744ecde8b8040ed5053a","tid":871630,"uid":56148,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T07:43:13.000Z","msg":"留名今晚睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我自己情況同樓主上半part 100% match"},{"pid":"7a3630957ac00a28c01ed140f14f92064ded68ab","tid":871630,"uid":153939,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4968b64e1f5c6e65d103744ecde8b8040ed5053a","tid":871630,"uid":56148,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T07:43:13.000Z","msg":"留名今晚睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我自己情況同樓主上半part 100% match"},"citedBy":